  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Ashborn have developed enough control over their elemental nature to direct it precisely. Smoldering Wounds prevents easy condition removal, meaning enemies who take Ignited from a Burning Fist are going to burn for at least one full round. Lava Spit handles targets trying to stay out of melee range. A summoner who keeps an Ashborn engaged with a single priority target will find it converts that target's hit points into fire conditions efficiently.</p>"
