    "tactics": "",
    "attacksNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Burning Fist [Combat]:</strong> Melee attack (Agi 3 + Melee Combat 5), Reach: 10 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 10 damage (Large, standard: 8 + 2) + 4 fire damage (Half DR)</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 16 damage (10 + 6 Str) + 4 fire damage; target gains Ignited condition</li>\n<li><em>Margin 3:</em> 16 damage + 4 fire damage; target gains Burning condition; no save</li>\n</ul></li>\n<li><strong>Lava Spit [Combat]:</strong> Ranged attack (Dex 2 + Ranged Combat 2), Range: 30 ft\n<ul>\n<li><em>Margin 1:</em> 6 fire damage (Half DR); target gains Singed</li>\n<li><em>Margin 2:</em> 10 fire damage; target gains Ignited; no save</li>\n</ul></li>\n</ul>",
    "specialAbilitiesNotes": "<ul>\n<li><strong>Heat Aura:</strong> Creatures starting their turn within 5 feet take 4 fire damage (Half DR).</li>\n<li><strong>Powerful Build.</strong></li>\n<li><strong>Smoldering Wounds:</strong> When the Ashborn deals Ignited or Burning condition to a target, that target cannot remove the condition through normal means (dropping and rolling, ally assistance) for 1 round. Magical healing still removes it.</li>\n</ul>",
